    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>NEW YORK</p>
        <p>GOVERNMENT OFFICES --</p>
        <p>Federal, state and municipal offices closed.</p>
        <p>POST OFFICES --</p>
        <p>Express Mail only; main post office on Eighth Avenue at 32nd Street is open.</p>
        <p>BANKS -- Option to close.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>NEW YORK</p>
        <p>GOVERNMENT OFFICES --</p>
        <p>Federal, state and municipal offices closed.</p>
        <p>POST OFFICES --</p>
        <p>Express Mail only; main post office on Eighth Avenue at 32nd Street is open.</p>
        <p>BANKS -- Option to close.</p>
        <p>PARKING -- Alternate-side regulations will be suspended. Meters still in effect unless otherwise noted.</p>
        <p>SANITATION -- No pickups and no street cleaning.</p>
        <p>SCHOOLS -- Closed in New  York City; option to close elsewhere.</p>
        <p>FINANCIAL MARKETS -- Stock markets are open, bond markets are closed.</p>
        <p>TRANSPORTATION -- New York City subways and buses will operate on a weekday schedule. The Long Island Rail Road and Metro-North are on a weekday schedule.</p>
        <p>NEW JERSEY</p>
        <p>GOVERNMENT OFFICES -- Federal and state offices closed.</p>
        <p>POST OFFICES -- Express Mail only.</p>
        <p>BANKS -- Option to close.</p>
        <p>SCHOOLS -- Option to close.</p>
        <p>TRANSPORTATION -- New Jersey Transit rail service will operate on a weekday schedule. PATH trains will operate on a modified weekday schedule.</p>
        <p>CONNECTICUT</p>
        <p>GOVERNMENT OFFICES -- Federal and state offices closed.</p>
        <p>POST OFFICES -- Express Mail only.</p>
        <p>BANKS -- Option to close.</p>
        <p>SCHOOLS -- Closed.</p>
        <p>TRANSPORTATION -- Metro-North trains will operate on a weekday schedule.</p>
      </block>
    </body.content>
